author: Brian Heater
title: Eventbrite pulls protest listings over violations of stay-at-home orders
description: Earlier this week, Facebook confirmed that it had begun pulling down select COVID-19 protests, citing violations of State-enforced social distancing. The social media giant was attempting a sort of diplomacy noting that all rallies/protests would be assessed …
